org.mitre.openid.connect.client.service.impl

Class HybridClientConfigurationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.openid.connect.client.service.impl.HybridClientConfigurationService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientConfigurationService

    public class HybridClientConfigurationService
extends Object
implements ClientConfigurationService
    Houses both a static client configuration and a dynamic client configuration service in one object. Checks the static service first, then falls through to the dynamic service. Provides configuration passthrough for the template, registered client service, whitelist, and blacklist for the dynamic service, and to the static service's client map.
    Author:
    jricher
